lit en Ukraine impacte les rituels \u00e9tatiques russes, tandis qu'en France, le d\u00e9bat sur le chiffrement des communications et la protection de l'enfance s'intensifie.\n\n**EN:** The cyber threat landscape on May 10, 2026, is characterized by an increase in attacks on software supply chains and AI infrastructure, alongside the exploitation of critical Linux kernel vulnerabilities (Copy Fail, DirtyFrag). A strong trend targets development environments using sophisticated malware like Quasar Linux RAT (QLNX). Simultaneously, geopolitical pressure from the Ukraine conflict impacts Russian state rituals, while in France, debates over communication encryption and child protection intensify.\n", "object_refs": ["identity--1dc08bb0-1b9a-5415-b578-aacc99ac99ea"], "abstract": "Strategic | Daily brief (2026-05-10)", "labels": ["strategic", "viglintel", "daily-report"], "object_marking_refs": ["marking-definition--613f2e26-407d-48c7-9eca-b8e91df99dc9", "marking-definition--ad15a0cd-55b6-4588-a14c-a66105329b92"]}, {"type": "relationship", "spec_version": "2.1", "id": "relationship--3fc612d2-3de7-5f92-afd4-26f8825e9655", "created": "2026-05-10T00:00:00Z", "modified": "2026-05-10T00:00:00Z", "created_by_ref": "identity--1dc08bb0-1b9a-5415-b578-aacc99ac99ea", "relationship_type": "related-to", "source_ref": "note--efec4315-3a64-5bc0-9ac8-3ad53564cc7f", "target_ref": "identity--1dc08bb0-1b9a-5415-b578-aacc99ac99ea", "description": "Strategic note linked to referenced object", "labels": ["strategic", "note-link", "viglintel", "daily-report"], "object_marking_refs": ["marking-definition--613f2e26-407d-48c7-9eca-b8e91df99dc9", "marking-definition--ad15a0cd-55b6-4588-a14c-a66105329b92"]}, {"type": "note", "spec_version": "2.1", "id": "note--24f99b59-bfe8-5f95-8800-b661adcc1097", "created": "2026-05-10T00:00:00Z", "modified": "2026-05-10T00:00:00Z", "created_by_ref": "identity--1dc08bb0-1b9a-5415-b578-aacc99ac99ea", "content": "## Summary\n**FR:** D\u00e9bat politique intense en France concernant l'affaiblissement potentiel du chiffrement de bout en bout pour faciliter la protection de l'enfance et les efforts de s\u00e9curit\u00e9 int\u00e9rieure.\n\n**EN:** Intense political debate in France regarding the potential weakening of end-to-end encryption to facilitate child protection and internal security efforts.\n\n## Context\n- Date: 2026-05-10\n- Sector: ['Gouvernement et D\u00e9fense'] / ['Government_and_Defense']\n- Theme: D\u00e9bat sur le chiffrement et la protection de l'enfance en France / Encryption and Child Protection Debate in France\n\n## Tags\nencryption, legislation, privacy\n\n## Sources\n- https://mastobot.ping.moi/@Bobe_bot/116547335714829637\n", "object_refs": ["identity--1dc08bb0-1b9a-5415-b578-aacc99ac99ea"], "abstract": "Geopolitical | D\u00e9bat sur le chiffrement et la protection de l'enfance en France (2026-05-10)", "external_references": [{"source_name": "source", "url": "https://mastobot.ping.moi/@Bobe_bot/116547335714829637"}], "labels": ["encryption", "legislation", "privacy", "geopolitical", "viglintel", "daily-report"], "object_marking_refs": ["marking-definition--613f2e26-407d-48c7-9eca-b8e91df99dc9", "marking-definition--ad15a0cd-55b6-4588-a14c-a66105329b92"]}, {"type": "relationship", "spec_version": "2.1", "id": "relationship--edba1f38-710b-548d-a486-a1c307219b2e", "created": "2026-05-10T00:00:00Z", "modified": "2026-05-10T00:00:00Z", "created_by_ref": "identity--1dc08bb0-1b9a-5415-b578-aacc99ac99ea", "relationship_type": "related-to", "source_ref": "note--24f99b59-bfe8-5f95-8800-b661adcc1097", "target_ref": "identity--1dc08bb0-1b9a-5415-b578-aacc99ac99ea", "description": "Geopolitical note linked to referenced object", "labels": ["encryption", "legislation", "privacy", "geopolitical", "note-link", "viglintel", "daily-report"], "object_marking_refs": ["marking-definition--613f2e26-407d-48c7-9eca-b8e91df99dc9", "marking-definition--ad15a0cd-55b6-4588-a14c-a66105329b92"]}, {"type": "note", "spec_version": "2